t]] confirmed 43 cases of COVID-19, all of them involved people who had travelled to Iran in February.<ref>{{cite news|author=Sara Al Shurafa|url=https://gulfnews.com/world/gulf/kuwait/kuwait-confirms-43-cases-of-coronavirus-all-coming-from-iran-1.1582789585309|title=Kuwait confirms 43 cases of coronavirus, all coming from Iran|date=27 February 2020|work=Gulf News|access-date=27 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227105047/https://gulfnews.com/world/gulf/kuwait/kuwait-confirms-43-cases-of-coronavirus-all-coming-from-iran-1.1582789585309|archive-date=27 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Germany, [[Norway]], Sweden and Spain also confirmed new cases involving individuals with previous travels to Iran.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.trust.org/item/20200227142333-5k62k/|title=Lebanon health ministry confirms third case of coronavirus, NNA reports|last=Foundation|first=Thomson Reuters|website=news.trust.org|access-date=27 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227153900/https://news.trust.org/item/20200227142333-5k62k/|archive-date=27 February 2020|url-status=live}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.swr.de/swraktuell/rheinland-pfalz/kaiserslautern/Neuer-Fall-in-Rheinland-Pfalz-Coronavirus-bei-Patienten-in-Kaiserslautern-festgestellt,corona-kaiserslautern-100.html|title=Coronavirus bei Patient in Kaiserslautern festgestellt|last=Aktuell|first=S. W. R.|last2=Aktuell|first2=S. W. R.|website=swr.online|language=de|access-date=27 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227170424/https://www.swr.de/swraktuell/rheinland-pfalz/kaiserslautern/Neuer-Fall-in-Rheinland-Pfalz-Coronavirus-bei-Patienten-in-Kaiserslautern-festgestellt,corona-kaiserslautern-100.html|archive-date=27 February 2020|url-status=live}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.fhi.no/nyheter/2020/tre-nye-personer-har-testet-positivt-pa-koronavirus/|title=Tre nye personer har testet positivt p\u00e5 koronavirus|website=Folkehelseinstituttet|language=no|access-da