's Rib Shack, a Firefighter's Journey}}</ref>\n* ''The Academy: Orange County Fire Authority Recruit Class 36'' (FOX reality TV 2009)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/the-academy/episodes/288385|title=The Academy - TV Guide|website=TVGuide.com}}</ref>\n* ''The Price of Fire. National film board of Canada. 1960. Excellent educational documentary.\n* ''[[The Triangle Factory Fire Scandal]]'' (1979)\n* ''Toxic Hot Seat'' (HBO 2013)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.toxichotseatmovie.com|title=Toxic Hot Seat Movie - Interior Design and Area Rug Home Decorating Blog|website=Toxic Hot Seat Movie}}</ref>\n* ''Toxic Soup: The Politics of Pollution'' (2011)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toxicsoupmovie.com|title=Toxic Soup|website=toxicsoupmovie.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[Triangle Fire]]'' (PBS American Experience 2011)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/americanexperience/films/triangle/|title=Triangle Fire - American Experience - PBS|website=www.pbs.org}}</ref>\n* ''Tunnel Inferno: Mont Blanc Tunnel Fire'' (TV Seconds From Disaster S01E02)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://secondsfromdisaster.net/s01e02-tunnel-inferno-mont-blanc-tunnel-fire/|title=Loading...|website=secondsfromdisaster.net}}</ref>\n* ''[[Twin Towers (film)|Twin Towers]]'' (2002)\n* ''Without Warning: Terror in the Towers'' (TV 1993)\n* ''[[World Trade Center (film)|World Trade Center]]'' (2006)\n* ''The Women of Ground Zero'' (2002)\n{{div col end}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Fire fighting}}\n\n[[Category:Firefighting-related lists]]\n[[Category:Films about firefighting|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of films by topic|Firefighting]]\n", "name_user": "Whitleyfilms", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:Added the film's website.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_firefighting_films"}
